data.description: Welcome to your dream Meadow Pointe residence! This charming two-story home offers three spacious bedrooms, two and a half baths, and a convenient one-car garage. Nestled in a prime location, you'll enjoy easy access to Lackland AFB, highways, top-rated schools, and shopping centers, making daily life a breeze. Step inside to discover a beautiful interior, featuring a stunning kitchen adorned with all matching black appliances and 36-inch high cabinets, providing both style and functionality. The open layout flows seamlessly into a cozy living space, perfect for relaxation or entertainment. Throughout the home, you'll find beautiful features that add character and warmth. With its thoughtful layout, modern amenities, and superb location, this Meadow Pointe gem promises to be your oasis, providing the ideal blend of comfort and convenience. Don't miss the chance to make this wonderful property your new home.
